snippet.title: What 's Bugsted. Demo game and serie. Help them back to the moon
snippet.description:
Bugsteds landed on planet Earth by accident. Their only goal is to get back to the moon and they desperately need your help! Lead these irreverent and undisciplined little creatures on their way home through 100 exciting game levels! Make sure that BOMMBA explodes in the right spot, that JUMMPA lands safely after his giant jumps or that Mole has all it gets to dig a tunnel in a ground full o mines. And look out for those Zombies!
